## SDK Installation

Install the Polaris Pay SDK via npm:

```bash
npm install @polaris-pay/sdk
```

## Setup

```javascript
import { PolarisClient } from "@polaris-pay/sdk";

const client = new PolarisClient({
  network: "mainnet",
  apiKey: "YOUR_API_KEY"
});
```

